-- How to add Dependency into Maven --

<repositories>
</repositories>

<dependencies>
</dependencies>

1. Navigate to pom.xml

2. In the project create tags: 
<dependencies>
</dependencies>

3. Add yout Dependency bettween tags
<dependencies>
__your_dependency__
</dependencies>


Example:

    <dependencies>

        <!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.appium/java-client -->
        <dependency>
            <groupId>io.appium</groupId>
            <artifactId>java-client</artifactId>
            <version>5.0.4</version>
        </dependency>

        <!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/junit/junit -->
        <dependency>
            <groupId>junit</groupId>
            <artifactId>junit</artifactId>
            <version>4.12</version>
            <scope>test</scope>
        </dependency>


    </dependencies>